        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】Lenovo Legion Go S 正式發布，首款官方認證 SteamOS 手提遊戲機</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/lenovo-legion-go-s/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-legion-go-s</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/lenovo-legion-go-s/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 12:20:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Lenovo Legion Go]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Lenovo Legion Go S]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285835</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 CES 2025 消費科技展當中 Lenovo 宣佈推出全新手提遊戲裝置 Legion Go S，以 USD499（約港幣 HK$3,892）售價推出，並成為首款獲 Valve 認可並搭載 Steam Deck 系統 SteamOS 的第三方產品。產品亦提供搭載 Windows 的版本，為用户提供更多選擇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285836" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/247466_ces_2025_leno-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/247466_ces_2025_leno-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/247466_ces_2025_leno.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285837" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/legiongosjpg-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/legiongosjpg-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/legiongosjpg.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>這款重量只有約 730g 的 Legion Go S 是 Lenovo 現有 8 吋手提遊戲機的改進版本。與之前設計不同，新機去除了可拆卸手掣和支架，改用輕巧且舒適的握把設計。Legion Go S 還配備 120Hz 可變更新率螢幕，有助於提升低幀率遊戲的流暢度，並搭載 Lenovo 獨家 AMD Ryzen Z2 Go 晶片，熒幕解像度為 1920 x 1200，致力於平衡性能與續航。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285838" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/legiongos2jpg-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/legiongos2jpg-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/legiongos2jpg.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Legion Go S 亦對玩家反映的不足進行了全面優化，例如新增可配置 RGB 燈光、改良觸控板設計，以及提供更大 55Wh 電池容量和可調節的扳機行程控制桿。Legion Go S 保留了雙 USB 4 插口，進一步增強其擴展性。</p><h4></h4><p>Lenovo 表示 SteamOS 型號將於 5 月推出，而 Windows 版本則會於 1 月率先上市。Windows 版本售價為 USD729.99（約港幣 HK$5,693），配置 32GB 記憶體和 1TB 儲存空間，而 SteamOS 型號則定價 USD499.99（約港幣 HK$3,892），擁有 16GB 記憶體和 512GB 儲存空間。此外，玩家亦可選擇售價 USD599.99（約港幣 HK$4,680）的 Windows 型號，其搭載 16GB 記憶體和 1TB 儲存空間。</p><p>Valve 和 Lenovo 的合作仍在進行中，SteamOS 型號的整合工作尚未完全完成。包括新觸控板、陀螺儀以及 RGB 燈光和功率配置等功能，仍需持續調整。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/7/24338028/lenovo-legion-go-s-steam-windows">The Verge</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/lenovo-legion-go-s/notebook/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【教學】日元跌破新低旅遊好時機，iPhone 鎖定畫面一鍵計算兑換率</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/travel-calculating-money-exchange-rate/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=travel-calculating-money-exchange-rate</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/travel-calculating-money-exchange-rate/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 11:59:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[實用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅遊]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS 18.2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1284867</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>農曆新年假期將至，大家有沒有旅遊的打算呢？最近日元又跌破新低，截稿前 100 日元約等於 4.92 港元，小編也「心鬱鬱」想去日本了。今日小編想和大家分享一個實用小技巧，能夠在 iPhone 鎖定畫面一鍵計算兑換率，想在消費時快速換算港元價格就要看下去了。</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="0108 (2)(2)" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1044976294?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="0108 (2)" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1044971084?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p>iOS 18 前 iPhone 鎖定畫面下方預設為「電筒」和「相機」。更新至 iOS 18 後，用家可更改為各種自訂功能。小編數學不太好，計算匯率時經常會「一頭煙」。設定了這個功能之後，就不用再費神計算。啟用「換算」功能後，無須解鎖即可在鎖定畫面直接開啟計算機，迅速進行匯率換算，省時又高效。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285860" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_3-535x580.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_3-535x580.jpg 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_3.jpg 830w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一鍵即可計算外幣匯率</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285861" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1112-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1112-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1112.png 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即時可以計算匯率</p><h2>Step 1 長按鎖定畫面開啟設定</h2><p>如果你的 iPhone 有密碼，你需要先解鎖 iPhone，然後開啟鎖定頁面，長按任意位置直至出現「Customize」選項後點擊「Customize」。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_6-535x580.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_6-535x580.jpg 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_6.jpg 830w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲解鎖後長按畫面，點擊「Customize」</p><h2>Step 2 更改工具為計算機</h2><p>現時你可以按照個人需求，選擇移除電筒或相機快捷鍵，之後點擊「+」，改為使用計算機。完成設定後點擊右上角的「Done」。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285899" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_7-1-535x580.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_7-1-535x580.jpg 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_7-1.jpg 830w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲移除其中一個工具，之後點擊「+」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285918" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_8-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_8-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_8.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「計算機」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285920" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_9-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_9-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/iphone_9.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲看見 icon 變成計算機後，你就可以點擊左上角的「Done」</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/travel-calculating-money-exchange-rate/life-tech/travel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
