        <item>
            <title>【CES2025】無內置電池、毋須充電的無線鍵盤   Lenovo 新產品可靠環境光供電</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/wirelesskeyboard/notebook/notebook-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wirelesskeyboard</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/08/wirelesskeyboard/notebook/notebook-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 09:29:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Notebook 配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[CES2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lenovo]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285843</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>好多無線鍵盤用家，都要不時為鍵盤充電或更換電池，而 Lenovo 在 CES 2025 消費科技展就展示了一款 Self-Charging Bluetooth Keyboard 藍牙鍵盤，拋棄了傳統電池設計，透過光電面板和環境光線實現自我充電，成為科技與環保的融合。我們就等記者 Edward 帶大家一齊到現場睇睇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285850" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852403-694x440.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="440" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852403-694x440.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852403.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285853" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/05vxhciubawazdjw3wau-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/05vxhciubawazdjw3wau-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/05vxhciubawazdjw3wau.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>鍵盤核心技術在於結合光伏發電與超級電容器。鍵盤頂部設有高效能光電面板，可持續吸收太陽光或室內環境光，並通過超級電容器儲存能量。相比傳統的鋰電池，超級電容器擁有更長的壽命，能承受數十萬次充放電循環，而鋰電池通常僅能維持約五年。</p><p>自充電鍵盤的設計亦相當實用與現代化。鍵盤為全尺寸設計，具有抗潑灑功能和三區域佈局，方便用户進行自訂設置。同時產品支援藍牙連接，最多可連接三部裝置，亦提供 USB-C 連接選項，該連接口隱藏於鍵盤頂部可拆卸蓋內。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285848" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010851816-430x580.jpg" alt="" width="430" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010851816-430x580.jpg 430w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010851816.jpg 668w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 430px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配合 App 可瞭解鍵盤目前感光的程度</p><p><figure id="attachment_1285851" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1285851" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1285851" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852427-694x447.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="447" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852427-694x447.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025010852427.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1285851" class="wp-caption-text">▲我們的記者用手指遮敝感應器的情況下，程式感應的光度會自然變得較小</figcaption></figure></p><p>這款鍵盤還可以搭配 Lenovo Accessories and Display Manager 應用程式使用，用户可在螢幕上查看亮度指示以及即時電力狀態。無需更換電池的設計，除減少電子垃圾的產生，亦為用户省下額外成本，對環保與經濟效益均帶來正面影響。</p><p>多年來，我們已見過多種太陽能設備，但僅近年才有實用的替代方案出現，例如染料敏化太陽能電池等新技術。雖然這些技術距離用於筆記型電腦或手機仍需時日，但對於鍵盤與滑鼠等小型裝置，卻已顯得成熟可行。</p><p>資料來源：Unwire.hk<br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
